text: Edaina Jaragocchu is a 2019 Indian Telugu-language action thriller film directed by K Ramakanth and starring Vijay Raja, Pooja Solanki, Bobby Simha, and Sasha Singh in the lead roles.https://www.deccanchronicle.com/entertainment/tollywood/120419/a-comic- thriller.html This film marks the debut of Sivaji Raja's son, Vijay Raja.https://www.thehansindia.com/cinema/tollywood/shivaji-rajas-son- debuts-553143https://www.thehansindia.com/cinema/tollywood/sivaji-rajas-son- debut-flick-523549https://www.thehansindia.com/cinema/edaina-jaragocchu-movie- teaser-talk-523112 The director Ramakanth previously worked as an assistant to Chandra Sekhar Yeleti. The film was launched on 11 July 2018 and the launch was attended by several celebrities. == Cast == *Vijay Raja as Jai *Pooja Solanki as Sasi *Bobby Simha as Kali * Sasha Singh as Baby *Nagendra Babu *Viva Raghav *Prudhviraj *Jhansi *Ajay Ghosh *Vennela Kishore in a special appearance ==Soundtrack== Soundtrack was composed by Srikanth Pendyala. *Kavale - Aparna Nandan *Anubavinchu - Prudhvi Chandran, Sweekar Agasthi *Adigo - Gold Devaraj, Lipsika *Cheliya - Yazin Nizar == Release == The Times of India gave the film a rating of one-and-a-half out of five stars and wrote that " A weak story and screenplay make the film an unfortunate bore altogether". News Minute wrote "The movie is such a bad mishmash that the title might as well apply to you, the audience. Anything could happen to your fused brains".https://www.thenewsminute.com/article/edaina-jaragochu-review- jarring-horror-comedy-which-neither-scary-nor-funny-107720 ==References== ==External links== * Category:2019 films Category:2010s Telugu-language films Category:Indian films Category: Indian thriller films Category:2019 thriller films
